{"title_page": "Avinav yadav", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date = February 2020}}\n {{short description|Nepalese cricketer}}\n{{Infobox cricketer|name=Avinav yadav|country=Nepal|fullname=Avinav yadav|birth_date={{Birth date and age|2004|03|16|df=yes}}|birth_place=Madar,siraha-16, Nepal|heightft=5|heightinch=5|heightm=5.5|nickname=Avi|batting=Right-handed|bowling=[[ Right-arm off-break]]|role=[[All-rounder]]|source=http://m.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/1174100.html|date=28 January|year=2019}}'''Avinav yadav''' (born 16 march 2004) is an Nepalese [[Cricket|cricketer]] .[1] He made his debut for Kathmandu goldens in the 2019 Dhangadhi Premier League (DPL) 11 February 2019.\n\n\n<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/1174100.html|title=Avinav Yadav|last=Yadav|first=Avinav|date=ESPNCricinfo|website=ESPNCricinfo|url-status=live|archive-url=http://m.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/1174100.html|archive-date=Today|access-date=2020-04-25}}</ref>\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date = February 2020}}\n {{short description|Nepalese cricketer}}\n{{Infobox cricketer|name=Avinav yadav|country=Nepal|fullname=Avinav yadav|birth_date={{Birth date and age|2004|03|16|df=yes}}|birth_place=Madar,siraha-16, Nepal|heightft=5|heightinch=5|heightm=5.5|nickname=Avi|batting=Right-handed|bowling=[[ Right-arm off-break]]|role=[[All-rounder]]|source=http://m.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/1174100.html|date=28 January|year=2019}}'''Avinav yadav''' (born 16 march 2004) is an Nepalese [[Cricket|cricketer]] .[1] He made his debut for Kathmandu goldens in the 2019 Dhangadhi Premier League (DPL) 11 February 2019.\n", "name_user": "Avinav yadav", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Avinav_yadav"}
